It supports reading & writing of 1D and 2D barcodes in digital images and PDF files. Supported barcode types: Australian Post, Aztec, Code11, Code39, Code128, Codabar, DataMatrix, EAN-8, EAN-13, Han Xin, GS1, Industrial standard 2 of 5, Interleaved 2 of 5, Intelligent Mail, PDF417, microPDF417, QR Code, Royal Mail, GS1 RSS, UPC-A, UPC-E, etc.
